1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,800
Science has a clearer story about astrocytes roles than social media does.

2
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:11,200
Astrocytes are star-shaped cells in your brain, but they do way more than just look pretty.

3
00:00:11,200 --> 00:00:15,600
They regulate blood flow, support neurons, and maintain the blood-brain barrier.

4
00:00:15,600 --> 00:00:20,800
Studies show astrocytes can even influence your mood and cognition by releasing chemicals.

5
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:22,800
But remember, research is ongoing.

6
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:25,600
Their full potential is still a mystery.

7
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:28,000
Want to unlock more brain secrets?

